article_title: Concordia Academy crazy for the '50s during Lutheran Schools Week
article_text: Her coach, pop star Pharrell Williams, had lots of kind things to say about Huston, who placed third. “Hannah’s been just awesome to work with. She’s cute and always making funny faces,” Williams said. “She’s jokey and fun and bubbly and just has the best outlook.”

og.description: Nearly 2,300 Lutheran Church-Missouri Synod preschools, elementary schools and high schools celebrated last week with open houses, salutes and observances.
